# The Opus Match – Architecture

## Vision

The Opus Match is a premium mobile match-3 puzzle game inspired by cue sports, luxury interiors and elegant design.

## Core Systems

* Board Engine
* Match Detection
* Gravity Engine
* Level Loader
* Power-Up System
* Estate Hub
* Save System
* Audio Manager
* UI Manager

## Design Principles

* Premium over flashy
* Mobile-first
* Data-driven levels
* Modular code
* Fast loading
* Easy to expand

